OL,4,CLong Covid pay decision for key workers
OL,5,Ccould take a year
OL,6, A decision about whether key workers
OL,7, with long Covid should get compensation
OL,8, could take more than a year, government
OL,9, advisers have told the BBC.
OL,11,FIt comes after 65 MPs and peers wrote
OL,12,Fto Boris Johnson asking for the illness
OL,13,Fto be made an "occupational disease".
OL,15,FMore than a million people in the UK
OL,16,Fare thought to have long Covid,
OL,17,Fincluding over 120,000 healthcare
OL,18,Fworkers.
OL,20,FThe government says it is committed to
OL,21,Fsupporting people through the pandemic.
